name: MCSC(MiniCubeSavesCubemas)
description:
Note: It may take some time to load. Sorry about that.

How to play - 

Move Left; Left arrow key

Move Right: Right arrow key

Jump: Up arrow key

Double jump: Double press Up arrow key

Story: Canta has been captured by the mean and evil Crinch! It is your job to save Canta so Cubemas can go on!
